-- Hamas Leader to Visit Iran Upon Ahmadinejad Invite, Fars Reports
-- B y   L a d a n e   N a s s e r i
-- 2012-01-25T15:08:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-25/hamas-leader-to-visit-iran-upon-ahmadinejad-invite-fars-reports.html
Ismail Haniyeh, the top Hamas leader
in the  Gaza Strip , has received an invitation from Iranian
President  Mahmoud Ahmadinejad  and will visit Tehran,  Fars  said,
citing the group’s foreign affairs minister, Mohammed Awad.  Awad didn’t say when the trip would take place and what
topics will be discussed by the two men, according to the state-
run news agency.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ladane Nasseri in Dubai at 
 lnasseri@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  